Package com.sterlingcommerce.woodstock.callout

Contains CallOut Framework Classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISCCallOutManager
    This interface defines methods which the application has to implement if they are not using the database entities provided by platform.
    ISCVotingResolver
    This interface provides methods that need to be implemented by the application for each callout.
    SCCallOutConsts
    This interface defines Constants used in the CallOut Framework Sai Praveen
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SCBasicVotingResolver
    This voting resolver will proceed to the next unit if the execution of a unit is successful and return to the calling code if an Exception or RuntimeException or TimeOut occurs while executing the unit.
    SCCallOut
    This class holds all the callout metadata and has getters and setters for the callout metadata praveen
    SCCallOutDefaultImpl
    This class is a composite of the callout metadata.
    SCCallOutHelper
    This class contains methods to get the proxy for a given callout and executing the implementations for the callout sanumukonda
    SCCallOutResponse
    This is the response of every callout implementation praveen
    SCCallOutUnit
    This class holds all the callout implementation metadata and has getters and setters for the callout implementation details praveen
    SCCountingVotingResolver
    This voting resolver will proceed if the execution of a unit is successful or not.
    SCVotingResponse
    This is the response returned by implementations of ISCVotingResolver#validateUnitResponse(SCCallOutResponse, String) sanumukonda
